title: Vols rally to 38-31 win over No. 19 Georgia; Chubbs injured
text:
> Top News Vols rally to 38-31 win over No. 19 Georgia; Chubbs injured Tennessee quarterback Joshua Dobbs (11), running back Alvin Kamara (6) and Tennessee running back Jalen Hurd (1) celebrate after their team defeated Georgia won 38-31 in an NCAA college football game Saturday, Oct. 10, 2015, in Knoxville, Tenn.
